casebody.data:
No. 09-9362. Louis Robenson, Petitioner v. Walter A. McNeil, Secretary, Florida Department of Corrections. 559 U.S. 1104, 130 S. Ct. 2408,

176 L. Ed. 2d 920,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 3786. May 3, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Florida dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Same case below, 28 So. 3d 45.
